          b reduces or eliminates such
          cyclings under <ENAMEX TYPE="LAW">LD 12</ENAMEX>:<NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">12</NUMEX> (compare the raw data for 
          cry +v 
          cry 
          b for example, in Figure <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">3a</TIMEX>, <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">3b</TIMEX>, or
