        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">records</ENAMEX> within a given <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">group</ENAMEX> (which varied as to <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">body</ENAMEX> part,
        
        luc <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">reporter</ENAMEX> type, and 
        cry allele) were obtained; and such
