        Maximum <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Entropy Spectral Analysis</ENAMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">MESA</ENAMEX>) was employed to
        estimate the period of a rhythm, i.e., for a given
        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">time</ENAMEX>-course previously determined to be significantly
